<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/fonts.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/aboutusEn_style.css">
</head>

<body>

    <!-- ============================== -->
    <!-- HEADER: Include header partial -->
    <!-- ============================== -->
    <%- include('./partials/headerEn.ejs') %>

    <!-- ============================== -->
    <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
    <!-- ============================== -->
    <main>

        <!-- ============================== -->
        <!-- SECTION: About Us -->
        <!-- ============================== -->
        <section class="section">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>
                We are a small team working on the design and production of board games.
                Our focus is on creating new experiences and turning ideas into real products.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- ============================== -->
        <!-- SECTION: What We Build -->
        <!-- ============================== -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>What We Build</h2>
            <p>
                We design and produce board games, game prototypes, and tools for game-centered
                experiences. Our goal is to create products that are both entertaining and
                offer a unique experience for players.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- ============================== -->
        <!-- SECTION: Why We Do This -->
        <!-- ============================== -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>Why We Do This</h2>
            <p>
                We believe games can bring people together, enhance creativity,
                and create shared experiences. That's why we strive to turn new
                ideas into games that are worth experiencing.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- ============================== -->
        <!-- SECTION: How We Do It -->
        <!-- ============================== -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>How We Do It</h2>
            <p>
                Our work begins with ideation. Then the rules and mechanics of the game
                are designed, and prototypes are built. These prototypes are tested and
                refined until they reach a version ready for production or release.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- ============================== -->
        <!-- SECTION: Partnerships -->
        <!-- ============================== -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>What Partnerships We Accept</h2>
            <p>
                We are open to collaborating with game designers, publishers, manufacturers,
                and organizations looking to develop or produce board games and similar products.
                Collaboration can take the form of design, prototyping, or developing a new product.
            </p>
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- ============================== -->
    <!-- FOOTER: Include footer partial -->
    <!-- ============================== -->
    <%- include('./partials/footerEn.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>